y-featuring-burna-boy-little-simz-elyanna-and-tini-3786165">最近的Coldplay单曲“ We Pray”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-sampha-soulful-satellite-business-2-0-3776230">Sampha的“ Satellite Business 2.0”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wretch-32-on-new-single-black-and-british-and-upcoming-album-little-simz-3806246">Wertch 32的Comeback曲目“ Black和Bristital”</a>上。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-to-curate-evening-of-tate-modern-lates-this-month-3784059">去年，她还与Tate Modern联手</a>，策划了一个深夜音乐，讲习班和对话的夜晚。去年11月，西姆兹（Simz）还在曼彻斯特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-presents-busta-rhymes-with-the-global-icon-award-at-the-2024-mtv-emas-3811388">（MTV Europe）颁奖典礼上向全球偶像奖展示Busta Rhymes</a> 。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-sues-producer-and-sault-member-inflo-over-withheld-1-7million-loan-3846839">据报道，小西姆兹（Little Simz）最近以170万英镑的贷款起诉了生产商</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sault">苏尔特</a>成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/inflo">Inflo</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-to-play-one-off-orchestral-show-at-londons-meltdown-2025-as-first-line-up-announced-3848673">小西姆兹（Post Little Simz）在伦敦的《融化2025》中播放一次性的管弦乐节目，因为第一阵容宣布</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现。</p> ;
